{"tid":1920158,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"港鐵引入消毒機械人","createTime":"2020-03-11T09:25:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-11T09:41:26.000Z","uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"26d85cb74b2c2d202c80654d03e4ae45f2961004","tid":1920158,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T09:25:01.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎疫情持續，港鐵今日宣布引入自動操作的「雙氧水霧化消毒機械人」，為車廂及車站消毒。這個機械人是由港鐵與本地生物科技企業合作研發，以自動模式清潔一列八卡列車需時約四小時。港鐵表示，將會引進20部消毒機械人，在各車廠清潔列車。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/watch/?v=1806459359485154\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D1806459359485154&d=b5PQnn7rv2nSxMH%2F6z0stk4axDeVXns42j9POfnWuxs%3D&h=10d1854a\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/watch/?v=1806459359485154</a>"},{"pid":"6657aebf7506019a54f92280d4062f5c91e9d8bd","tid":1920158,"uid":5737,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T09:27:02.000Z","msg":"關我撚事咩<br />\n公開831cctv未呀？"},{"pid":"1160d920b41ff5dce9a4d653e723c559da21b6ff","tid":1920158,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T09:27:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OMKPUiT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOMKPUiT.png&h=82714701&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e881321ec101bc1747aa4927f44c6f18b5f4af4d","tid":1920158,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T09:28:58.000Z","msg":"港鐵與本地生物科研公司共同研發「雙氧水霧化機械人」，會引用20部機械人，在特殊情況、有需要深層清潔的情況下，用於消毒車廂及車站等。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵車務總監李家潤表示，有關的特殊情況，包括有確診患者在港鐵範圍內逗留，需要用作深層清潔，以及是當有乘客在車上嘔吐，會有清潔工人以稀釋漂白水清潔，再以機械人進行深層清潔，每晚的車廂消毒清潔仍由人手進行。<br />\n<br />\n他表示，早前有旺角東站港鐵職員確診新型肺炎病毒，當時已開始使用機械人消毒員工的後勤區域。<br />\n<br />\n鎧耀生物醫藥科技有限公司共同創辦人劉耀南說，雙氧水殺菌力高，揮發速度快，與漂白水等比較，雙氧水安全度更高。<br />\n<br />\n另外，港鐵引入一部口罩生產機，目前仍在設置無塵生產室的工作，預計最快今年下半年投產予員工使用。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1513778-20200311.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1513778-20200311.htm&d=b5PQnn7rv2nSxMH%2F6z0stk4axDeVXns42j9POfnWuxs%3D&h=86aa9452\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1513778-20200311.htm&h=5158098a\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1513778-20200311.htm</a>"},{"pid":"e6552a29d1e98e0b1dd33610e73df622667f2d2d","tid":1920158,"uid":119596,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T09:30:48.000Z","msg":"噴2野就深層清潔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲要點解係清潔工人先, 機械人後<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔係好明個次序"},{"pid":"092ff20702ceb518a332ed53b64a19c0d667bdb2","tid":1920158,"uid":11291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T09:31:11.000Z","msg":"啲狗一會唔會以為係鞋盒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e7e27b945955fb3009144fa2826bf630057f4b3","tid":1920158,"uid":237465,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T09:31:44.000Z","msg":"黨鐵咪撚扮好人<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.facebook.com/fans.hkgolden/videos/454600148528214/\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ffans.hkgolden%2Fvideos%2F454600148528214%2F&h=c8b898fb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"03fc8b57ef33a3b14458dc10dc81545e80650244","tid":1920158,"uid":165232,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e6552a29d1e98e0b1dd33610e73df622667f2d2d","tid":1920158,"uid":119596,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T09:30:48.000Z","msg":"噴2野就深層清潔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲要點解係清潔工人先, 機械人後<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔係好明個次序"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T09:32:43.000Z","msg":"= ="},{"pid":"7e1e3a7cff53cf044413d05da451cc1ffe1cc042","tid":1920158,"uid":339272,"like":0,